TCC(1)

NAME
    tcc - compile C programs with TinyCC

SYNOPSIS
    tcc [options] file ...

DESCRIPTION
    tcc is the SmallOS build of TinyCC. It can compile small C programs inside
    the system image.

    The shipped compiler is intended for experiments and demos, not for
    rebuilding the whole operating system from inside SmallOS.

FILES
    /usr/share/examples/tinycc
        Example C source files.

EXAMPLES
    tcc /usr/share/examples/tinycc/tccmini.c

SEE ALSO
    compiler_demo(1)
